      <body>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><seg rend="right" type="letterhead"><pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3175_0028"/><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="capitals"><hi rend="bold"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb255">Grand Hôtel</rs>, <foreign xml:lang="fra"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb50">Vienne</rs></foreign></hi></hi></hi></seg><seg rend="right" type="letterhead"><hi rend="pre-print"><hi rend="capitals"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb501">I., Kärntnerring 9</rs></hi></hi>.</seg><dateline rend="left"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb50">Wien</rs>, <date when="1906-06-03">3. Juni</date></dateline></opener><p>Herzlichen Dank, <salute>lieber Freund</salute>! Ich komme al<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>o <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L03246-1"/><date when="1906-06-04">Montag</date><note type="commentary" corresp="K_L03246-1"><ref type="schnitzler-tagebuch" target="1906-06-04" subtype="See"/>.
               </note><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><time>zwi<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chen 7 u. 8. Uhr</time>.</p><closer>Herzliche Grüße Dir und Deiner <rs type="person" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb2173">Frau</rs> von Deinem getreuen<lb/><signed>Paul Goldmann</signed></closer></div>
      </body>
